The paper discusses representation learning using deep neural networks for classification tasks. This topic falls under the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), and neural networks (cs.NE). Given that the paper focuses on improving classification performance using deep representation, it is most likely to belong to the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG), followed by computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
